<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Git Commit Bot</title>
    <style>
        body, h1, h2, h3, p, ol, li {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-weight: normal;
        
        }
                
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            flex-direction: row;

        }
        
        
        .container, .help {
            background: white;
            padding: 2em;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        
        h1, h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1em;
        }
        
        
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        
        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.5em;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-size: 1em;
        }
        
        
        button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75em;
            background: #007bff;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
        
        
        .help {
            background: white;
            padding: 2em;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        
        .help h2, .help h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .help p, .help ol {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .help ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .help li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }</style>
    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Git Commit Bot</h1>
        <form action="/start-commit" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="commitCount">Number of Commits:</label>
                <input type="number" id="commitCount" name="commitCount" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="commitYear">Commit Year:</label>
                <input type="number" id="commitYear" name="commitYear" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="username">GitHub Username:</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="token">GitHub Token:</label>
                <input type="text" id="token" name="token" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit">Start Commits</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="help">
        <h2>How to Use the Commit Bot</h2>
        <p>Follow these steps to use the Commit Bot:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Enter the number of commits you want to generate in the "Number of Commits" field.</li>
            <li>Enter the year for which you want the commits to be made in the "Year for Commits" field.</li>
            <li>Enter your GitHub username in the "GitHub Username" field.</li>
            <li>Generate a GitHub personal access token with the required permissions. See the instructions below for help.</li>
            <li>Enter the generated token in the "GitHub Token" field.</li>
            <li>Click the "Start Commits" button to begin the process.</li>
        </ol>
        <h3>Generating a GitHub Token</h3>
        <p>To generate a GitHub token:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Go to <a href="https://github.com/settings/tokens" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Settings</a>.</li>
            <li>Click on <strong>Generate new token</strong>.</li>
            <li>Select the scopes you need (e.g., <strong>repo</strong> for full control of private repositories).</li>
            <li>Click <strong>Generate token</strong>.</li>
            <li>Copy the generated token and paste it in the "GitHub Token" field.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</body>
</html>